      • addConfiguredAccessesToTree

        protected void addConfiguredAccessesToTree(org.dom4j.Element root,
                               String propFilePath)
        This method adds an accesscontrol tag to the given resource. Therefore it parses the attributes of the flag, allowed and denied tag to calculate the integer value.
        Parameters:
        root - The root element to add at the accesscontrol tag.
        propFilePath - The path to the property file.
